name: Verify if a student send request to join to teacher and teacher can accept it
description: A student can send request to join to a teacher using teacher email. Teacher can accept this request
descriptionHtml: A student can send request to join to a teacher using teacher email. Teacher can accept this request

testStage.description: A student can send request to join to a teacher using teacher email. Teacher can accept this request

steps.name: $("By.tagName: h1") should have(text "Create your teacher account")
$("#app > div.app-body > div > div > div.page-card__left-half > div > form > div:nth-of-type(2) > div > input") should be(visible)
$("#app > div.app-body > div > div > div.page-card__left-half > div > form > div:nth-of-type(2) > div > input") get wrapped element()
$("By.xpath: //input[@placeholder='Class code or Teacher’s email']") should be(visible)
$("By.xpath: //input[@placeholder='Class code or Teacher’s email']") send keys(autoTestTeacher4413721@gmail.com)
$("By.xpath: //ul[@class='teachers-list'].findBy(text "autoTestTeacher4413721@gmail.com")/By.xpath: .//div[2]/p") should(not exist or has text: not exist or text "Teacher accepted your request")
$("By.xpath: //div[@class='v-input v-input--hide-details theme--light v-text-field v-text-field--single-line v-text-field--is-booted']//div[@class='v-text-field__slot']/input") should be(visible)

$("By.xpath: //div[@class='v-input v-input--hide-details theme--light v-text-field v-text-field--single-line v-text-field--is-booted']//div[@class='v-text-field__slot']/input") send keys(NewTeacherAutotest187737540)
$("By.xpath: //i[@class='v-icon notranslate mdi mdi-close theme--dark']") should be(visible)
$("By.xpath: //header[@class='v-sheet theme--dark v-toolbar secondary']//i[@class='v-icon notranslate mdi mdi-dots-vertical theme--dark']") should be(visible)
$("By.xpath: //header[@class='v-sheet theme--dark v-toolbar secondary']//i[@class='v-icon notranslate mdi mdi-dots-vertical theme--dark']") click()
$("By.xpath: //button[@class='mt-4 v-btn v-btn--is-elevated v-btn--has-bg theme--light v-size--default error']/span") should be(visible)
$("By.xpath: //button[@class='mt-4 v-btn v-btn--is-elevated v-btn--has-bg theme--light v-size--default error']/span") click()
$("By.xpath: //div[@class='v-input v-input--hide-details theme--light v-text-field v-text-field--single-line v-text-field--is-booted']//div[@class='v-text-field__slot']/input") should be(visible)

$("By.xpath: //div[@class='v-input v-input--hide-details theme--light v-text-field v-text-field--single-line v-text-field--is-booted']//div[@class='v-text-field__slot']/input") send keys(NewTeacherAutotest187737540)
